titles.title: I'm Not Worthy, But I've Been Set Free

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
I'm not worthy, but I've been set free.
My sins before me, I leave at Calvary.
O Holy Spirit fill and keep me.
Let me walk and dance into this feast.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Seven days wave your branches.
Seven days praise and dances.
Seven days to rejoice with joy.
Let me walk and dance into this feast.

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
I'm set free and today I proclaim it.
I'm set free by the day of Atonement.
I'm set free, I give glory to Thee.
Let me walk and dance into this feast.

verse.name: v4
verse.lines:
Yo no soy digno pero libre soy.
Mis faltas veo pero vivo en la cruz.
Santo Espiritu llena y guiame.
Cantemos y dancemos en esta fiesta.

verse.name: v5
verse.lines:
Siete dias mecen las ramas,
Siete dias canto y danza,
Siete dias glorificale,
Cantemos y dancemos en esta fiesta.

verse.name: v6
verse.lines:
Soy libre, hoy lo proclamo, soy libre,
Por el dia de expiacion; soy libre,
Te doy gloria a ti;
Cantemos y dancemos en esta fiesta.
